name: Nike Air Max Pulse
detail: The Air Max Pulse pulls inspiration from the London music scene, bringing an underground touch to the iconic Air Max line. Its textile-wrapped midsole and vacuum-sealed accents keep 'em looking fresh and clean, while colours inspired by the London music scene give your look the edge. Point-loaded Air cushioning—revamped from the incredibly plush Air Max 270—delivers better bounce, helping you push past your limits.
